Description: Web UI for OpenVox infrastructure management
 OpenVox WebUI provides a modern web interface for managing and monitoring
 OpenVox infrastructure. Features include:
 .
  * PuppetDB integration with graphical dashboards
  * Node classification using dynamic groups
  * Facter-based node management
  * Role-based access control (RBAC)
  * YAML-based configuration
